Text:
Thanks for the ul!  It's always a treat to read almost anything by Alan Moore.

Have you ever read "Electric Warrior" drawn by Jim Baikie, I think written by Doug Moench?

Be fun to read those issues again!  ;-)

Please STFmarryville upload more volumes of Black Panther.... i want to delve into his origins etc...


I took time to go through all your 28 pages of torrents..all incredible and FREE stuff !!!. Thanks for all your help and generosity. Please more Black Panther!
